description: Try our easy to follow Baked Fish & Potato Rosti recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Baked Fish & Potato Rosti Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Remove fish and stand for 1 minute before opening. Transfer fish to serving plates with rosti. Top with salad mix and serve with lemon wedges.
